at the same company. I'm single.

263
00:16:45,629 --> 00:16:47,381
I always welcome blind dates.

264
00:16:51,051 --> 00:16:52,344
This place is huge.

265
00:16:52,428 --> 00:16:54,138
Well, where should we start?

266
00:16:54,221 --> 00:16:55,431
Well…

267
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:59,685
You two put up the banner.
I'll blow up the balloons.

268
00:17:02,187 --> 00:17:03,355
All right.

269
00:17:15,743 --> 00:17:19,496
Honestly, I saw your
credit card statement last time.

270
00:17:20,622 --> 00:17:23,250
-Why?
-It wasn't on purpose.

271
00:17:23,333 --> 00:17:26,253
