trying to earn more before the wedding.

282
00:18:03,999 --> 00:18:06,710
They say when a man gets married,
he becomes responsible.

283
00:18:07,294 --> 00:18:08,545
I'm impressed.

284
00:18:10,047 --> 00:18:11,131
Yes.

285
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:13,050
Of course.

286
00:18:14,927 --> 00:18:16,762
Move it a little more to the left.

287
00:18:16,845 --> 00:18:18,222
A little more.

288
00:18:18,305 --> 00:18:19,264
Here?

289
00:18:21,683 --> 00:18:24,436
Now this time, Hui-seon,
if you would move it

290
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,979
a little bit over to the right.

291
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,777
Excuse me.

292
00:18:32,277 --> 00:18:34,488
Is this really that important?

293
00:18:34,571 --> 00:18:35,906
Of course, it is.

294
00:18:35,989 --> 00:18:38,867
Doesn't it bother you
when these things aren't spaced evenly?

295
