303
00:19:22,619 --> 00:19:24,872
Everything's ready.
You can bring Na-eun over now.

304
00:19:25,455 --> 00:19:26,540
Why? Who is it?

305
00:19:27,291 --> 00:19:29,835
Well, my friends are nearby.

306
00:19:29,918 --> 00:19:32,713
