and they want us to stop by.

307
00:19:32,796 --> 00:19:35,591
Let's go see them since we're close by.

308
00:19:35,674 --> 00:19:36,800
Should we?

309
00:19:36,884 --> 00:19:39,094
Wait. Let me just make sure I look okay.

310
