315
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:05,913
And they say it's not bad
to party this way.

316
00:20:07,247 --> 00:20:10,459
Your college friends are pretty luxurious.

317
00:20:10,542 --> 00:20:12,419
Is this how you partied, too?

318
00:20:12,502 --> 00:20:15,339
Gosh, no.
I wouldn't hang out in a place like this.

319
00:20:15,422 --> 00:20:18,342
