like this. It's my first time.

320
00:20:18,425 --> 00:20:21,053
Then how did you know
the suite room is in the corner?

321
00:20:22,638 --> 00:20:25,849
It's fine. It's all in the past.

322
00:20:25,933 --> 00:20:27,935
I know you're not the same person.

323
00:20:30,687 --> 00:20:33,148
This is it, room 1355.

324
00:20:33,232 --> 00:20:34,399
Yes.

325
00:21:01,343 --> 00:21:03,136
HAPPILY EVER AFTER
JUN-HYEONG, NA-EUN

326
00:21:04,054 --> 00:21:05,180
